			"actions": [
				{
					"type": "comment",
					"text": "On start of the level:\n- Set time scale (the larger the value, the faster items will be thrown around)\n- Set GameManager time scale to 1.0 (so spawn timers will be relative to real time scale, not game time scale)\n- Call SpawnItem for waste items to start spawning\n- Call SpawnDistraction for distraction items to start spawning\n- Set and start timer for SpawnItem (interval in seconds in which a new waste item spawns)\n- Set and start timer for SpawnDistraction (interval in seconds in which a new distraction item spawns)"
				},
				{
					"id": "set-time-scale",
